video.title: Go! Mrs. Go!
video.synopsis: When her husband dies suddenly, aspiring writer Mrs. Go faces bankruptcy. While the future is uncertain, it's also hers to explore as never before.

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil lives with her husband, Joon-suk, in a town in Namhae. Joon-suk brings her a gift from a business trip and she feels happier than ever.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: After Joon-suk's sudden death, Mrs. Go Bong-shil hears about his  debt, which shocks her whole family. Yoon-young worries about her widowed mother.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Prosecutors come to Joon-suk's office in Itaewon, where Joon-tae and Kyung-soo are cleaning up, and accuse Joon-suk of smuggling cultural properties.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil drinks with Won-sook, who could pass for her husband's lover. Won-sook tells her about dates they had gone on, and Bong-shil feels betrayed.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil comes home to find out Joon-suk had smuggled cultural properties. As she struggles with the shocking news, a middle-aged couple visits her.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: When loan sharks flood Yoon-young's house, Kyung-soo gets angry and kicks them out. Jin-cheol comes and says he wants to take over Joon-suk's shop.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: In-young starts work at a convenience store, but does not like it one bit. Handsome Niki comes, but he does not like In-young being such a slacker.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Mrs. Go is overwhelmed by culture shock in Seoul. When an incident sends her to the police station, someone from her past comes to her aid.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: David rushes Bong-shil to the hospital, but she sneaks out of the ER after leaving him a memo. Without a place to go, she goes to a sauna in Itaewon.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: The family finds out that Bong-shil went to Seoul, where she has no friends or relatives. Out of concern, they go to the police station.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Yoon-young finds Bong-shil in Itaewon running her business. Her family asks her to come to Yoon-young's house, but Bong-Shil wants to be independent.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Just when Beom-soo is worried Bong-shil will see through him, the wind reveals a wound on his neck. She realizes the girl in front of her is Beom-soo.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil's kimbab and herbal tea are selling well. Dong-sik reports this to David. They think that there is something strange about the herbal tea.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil, Seok-cheon, and Man-geum get dragged to a warehouse in Itaewon and find David. David presses Bong-shil for information about her herbs.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Byung-geun disappears after Joon-suk's accident, and shows up near Itaewon. Bong-shil finds him in a run-down state, and senses something strange.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Just as Bong-shil, Won-sook, and Beom-soo come out of a spa, they run into Man-deuk. Man-deuk completely freaks out after recognizing Beom-soo.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Dong-sik learns Jin-cheol's shop used to be run by Bong-shil's husband. David hears about Joon-suk's death and debt, and thinks something is fishy.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: After finding out that Jin-cheol is dealing in paintings with the Yakuza, David goes to his shop, but Jin-cheol insists he does not deal in paintings.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: David happens to pass by a hotel and sees Bong-Shil's entire family celebrating her birthday. He has the manager bring out expensive wine as a gift.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: When Bong-shil's herbs are not growing well, she goes to an herb market to find out why, but gets no answers. She decides to seek out Dr. Wow.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: David tries to help Bong-shil open up a restaurant in a small alley in Itaewon. She refuses politely at first, but he makes an appealing offer.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Deciding to stop running away from her father, Man-deuk, Soo-ae (Beom-soo) visits him in Itaewon and reveals everything. Man-deuk is shocked.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: When Won-sook and Joon-tae visit the antique shop, they find that Jin-cheol had closed it. They are upset that he cleared out the shop with no notice.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil takes Joon-suk's broken watch and sits in sadness in her restaurant. Seeing her like this, David hugs her, and Bong-shil is surprised.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil visits Byung-geun with David. When he sees her, Byung-geun apologizes to her. The confession that soon comes from Byung-geun shocks her.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Jin-cheol raids Ri-soo’s club with Yakuza. Making a mess, they demand Ri-soo give them a highly sought-after piece of furniture. Ri-soo refuses.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Jin-cheol puts up posters about the lost furniture all over Itaewon.  Bong-shil calls Dong-sik. Jin-cheol finds out and Yakuza raid her restaurant.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil gathers the family and tells them the truth about Joon-suk's death. Shocked, they have mixed feelings about Jin-cheol. They feel betrayed.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: When In-young and Niki are on a date at a café, Jae-soo shows up and says he is In-young’s boyfriend. Taken aback, Niki takes him outside…
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Hoping David and Bong-shil will end up together, Dong-sik asks Soo-ae (Beom-soo) lots of questions. Soo-ae thinks that he likes her, and gets excited.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Man-deuk calls Geum-sil to a tea house and says that he will take care of her. There was something that happened between them 50 years ago...
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Soo-ae and Dong-sik get fairly close, and Dong-sik develops feelings for her. On her way to meet him, Soo-ae runs into a middle school friend…
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Bong-shil goes to Nami Island for a drive with David. They miss the last boat, and end up spending the night together on the island.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: Yoon-young is in a coma for days. She needs a transplant, but nobody is the same blood type. Bong-shil considers Yoon-young's biological mother.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Na-kyung, Yoon-young's birth mother, comes back to Korea from the US. In and out of consciousness, Yoon-young wants her mom, so she grabs her hands...
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Despite being very busy with business trips, Bong-shil publishes her own book. At the celebration, her family and friends congratulate her.
episodes.title: Episode 36
